<figure class="wp-block-table"><table><thead><tr><th>Governance Structure</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>On-chain Governance</td><td>Allows token holders to vote on proposals and decide the future of the network.</td></tr><tr><td>Council</td><td>Comprises elected representatives who propose and vote on changes to the protocol.</td></tr><tr><td>Community Governance</td><td>Involves community discussions and forums where ideas and improvements are shared and discussed.</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>



