<li><strong>Set up a Solana wallet</strong>: You&#8217;ll need a Solana wallet to store your NFTs and interact with the network. Popular options include Sollet or Phantom.</li>



<li><strong>Connect your wallet to the marketplace</strong>: Connect your wallet to the chosen marketplace to access the minting feature and manage your NFTs.</li>



<li><strong>Create your NFT</strong>: Prepare the artwork or content you want to turn into an NFT. Follow the marketplace&#8217;s instructions to mint your NFT, including setting a price and deciding on royalties.</li>



<li><strong>Promote and sell your NFT</strong>: Once your NFT is minted, promote it on social media and engage with the Solana NFT community to increase visibility and find potential buyers.</li>
